                    <span>I switched to Mac OS X from windows and this book was the only reason I stayed! It helped me get a grasp of Mac OS X quickly. It even gives you great tips that will increase your productivity. I used a coupon from UnderTag.com, so it was almost free for me too.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">THE Manual for OS X</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
